name: FiveCube (beta)
description: FiveCube is a game about a cube who is the most ordinary worker who fixes everything. He has a house in which he lives. In general, an ordinary inhabitant of his world. The game is NOT in release at the moment, but I will try to make it as high quality and faster as possible. Write comments under the project to make it clearer for me what you are missing in the game. The game was created by Godot Engine.
